              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Calibri' fontsize='18'>• Engagement alone is not sufficient to drive conversion  ​</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Calibri' fontsize='18'>​</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Calibri' fontsize='18'>• External conditions significantly shape user intent  ​</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Calibri' fontsize='18'>​</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Calibri' fontsize='18'>• Market maturity determines responsiveness to external factors  ​</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Calibri' fontsize='18'>​</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Calibri' fontsize='18'>• Higher conversion in developed markets is driven by efficiency, not engagement volume </run>
